    "An exception is PhraseMap [52], where a map metaphor is used to visualize the extracted technical phrases.",
    "Similar to our approach, they use a Gosper curve to create the layout.",
    "Different from topic-and entity-based approaches, embedding-based approaches typically employ dimensionality reduction techniques and use a scatter plot as their primary visualization [12], [16], [38], [43].",
    "One key distinction of the visualization between topic-based and embedding-based approaches is the unit of abstractions.",
    "In topic-based approaches, the unit of abstractions is \"bagof-words\" (topics) and their hierarchies."
